li\\u1ec7u. C&aacute;c ph&iacute;m c&oacute; \\u0111\\u1ed9 n\\u1ea3y t\\u1ed1t, c\\u1ea5u tr&uacute;c ch\\u1eafc ch\\u1eafn, \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o c\\u1ea3m gi&aacute;c &ecirc;m &aacute;i khi g&otilde; ph&iacute;m. \\u0110&egrave;n n\\u1ec1n LED b&ecirc;n d\\u01b0\\u1edbi b&agrave;n ph&iacute;m cho ph&eacute;p b\\u1ea1n d\\u1ec5 d&agrave;ng quan s&aacute;t trong m&ocirc;i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng thi\\u1ebfu &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng. Touchpad v\\u1eeba ph\\u1ea3i, b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t \\u0111\\u1ee7 tr\\u01a1n m\\u1ecbn \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t&aacute;c m\\u01b0\\u1ee3t m&agrave;, tho\\u1ea3i m&aacute;i.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<figure><img alt=\\\"M\\u00e1y t\\u00ednh x\\u00e1ch tay\\/ Laptop Acer Aspire 7 A715-42G-R05G (NH.QAYSV.007) | B\\u00e0n ph\\u00edm \\u00eam \\u00e1i\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/storage.googleapis.com\\/teko-gae.appspot.com\\/media\\/image\\/2022\\/7\\/4\\/20220704_808086ce-448a-43a5-9e2f-ce82859ac2e5.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/figure>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, chi\\u1ebfc laptop cao c\\u1ea5p c&ograve;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t&iacute;ch h\\u1ee3p t&iacute;nh n\\u0103ng b\\u1ea3o m\\u1eadt b\\u1eb1ng khu&ocirc;n m\\u1eb7t, cho ph&eacute;p ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng m\\u1edf m&aacute;y, m\\u1edf kh&oacute;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh nhanh ch\\u1ec9 trong v&agrave;i gi&acirc;y. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi t\\u0103ng c\\u01b0\\u1eddng kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng b\\u1ea3o m\\u1eadt c\\u1ee7a th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o an to&agrave;n cho d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u l\\u01b0u tr\\u1eef tr&ecirc;n m&aacute;y c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<figure><img alt=\\\"M\\u00e1y t\\u00ednh x\\u00e1ch tay\\/ Laptop Acer Aspire 7 A715-42G-R05G (NH.QAYSV.007) | Dung l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng pin 48Wh\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/storage.googleapis.com\\/teko-gae.appspot.com\\/media\\/image\\/2022\\/7\\/4\\/20220704_72f9ad81-5c9d-43fa-88de-8a5751698ee9.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/figure>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Chi\\u1ebfc laptop s\\u1eed d\\u1ee