(407, '1', 'sc_admin/product/create', 'POST', '::1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/108.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '{\"kind\":\"0\",\"descriptions\":{\"en\":{\"name\":\"Laptop MSI Modern 15 A11M (i5-1155G7\\/RAM 8GB\\/512GB SSD\\/ Windows 11)\",\"keyword\":\"Laptop MSI Modern\",\"description\":\"CPU: Intel Core i5-1155G7\",\"content\":\"<h3><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/phongvu.vn\\/c\\/laptop\\\"><strong>Laptop<\\/strong><\\/a><strong>&nbsp;MSI Modern 15 A11M-1024VN (X&aacute;m) s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu hi\\u1ec7u n\\u0103ng m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ebfn t\\u1eeb b\\u1ed9 vi x\\u1eed l&yacute; Core 5 th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ee9 11. V\\u1edbi v\\u1ebb ngo&agrave;i ho&agrave;n thi\\u1ec7n cao c\\u1ea5p c&ugrave;ng thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf g\\u1ecdn nh\\u1eb9 hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i c\\u1ee7a MSI h\\u1ee9a h\\u1eb9n s\\u1ebd l&agrave; s\\u1ef1 l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn \\u0111&aacute;ng tin c\\u1eady v\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u1ec3 c&ugrave;ng b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h&agrave;nh trong c&ocirc;ng vi\\u1ec7c c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y.&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><strong>Thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf m&agrave;u x&aacute;m \\u0111\\u1eb3ng c\\u1ea5p, nh\\u1ecf g\\u1ecdn d\\u1ec5 d&agrave;ng mang theo<\\/strong><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>V\\u1ecf b\\u1ecdc b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i chi\\u1ebfc laptop MSI Modern 15 A11M-1024VN \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf t\\u1eeb ch\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec7u nguy&ecirc;n kh\\u1ed1i c&ugrave;ng v\\u1edbi gam m&agrave;u x&aacute;m hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i ph&ugrave; h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi m\\u1ecdi kh&ocirc;ng gian l&agrave;m vi\\u1ec7c c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, chi\\u1ebfc laptop MSI n&agrave;y c&ograve;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 ch\\u1eafc ch\\u1eafn b\\u1edfi l\\u1edbp v\\u1ecf ngo&agrave;i c\\u1ee9ng c&aacute;p h\\u1ea1n ch\\u1ebf c&aacute;c t&aacute;c \\u0111\\u1ed9ng t\\u1eeb b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i nh\\u01b0 va ch\\u1ea1m m\\u1ea1nh, ch\\u1ed1ng tr\\u1ea7y x\\u01b0\\u1edbc,...<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<figure><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/storage.googleapis.com\\/teko-gae.appspot.com\\/media\\/image\\/2022\\/3\\/29\\/20220329_f64dc95a-2b16-4c4f-be34-53ac84f04bd6.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/figure>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>MSI Modern 15 A11M-1024VN s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf nguy&ecirc;n kh\\u1ed1i g\\u1ecdn nh\\u1eb9 v\\u1edbi k&iacute;ch th\\u01b0\\u1edbc 35.68 x 23.375 x 1.69 cm c&ugrave;ng tr\\u1ecdng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng 1.6kg, s\\u1eb5n s&agrave;ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 b\\u1ea1n mang theo \\u0111\\u1ebfn b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 \\u0111&acirc;u. B&ecirc;n c\\u1ea1nh \\u0111&oacute;, chi\\u1ebfc laptop n&agrave;y c&ograve;n c&oacute; v\\u1ebb ngo&agrave;i sang tr\\u1ecdng kh&ocirc;ng k&eacute;m ph\\u1ea7n thanh l\\u1ecbch.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><strong>M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh 15.6 inch Full HD s\\u1eafc n&eacute;t, vi\\u1ec1n m\\u1ecfng t\\u1ea1o g&oacute;c r\\u1ed9ng&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Laptop MSI Modern 15 A11M-1024VN v\\u1edbi m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh chu\\u1ea9n 15.6 inch h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng hi\\u1ec3n th\\u1ecb t\\u1ed1t c&ugrave;ng l&uacute;c nhi\\u1ec1u ph\\u1ea7n m\\u1ec1m. Chi\\u1ebfc laptop MSI n&agrave;y c&ograve;n c&oacute; \\u0111\\u1ed9 ph&acirc;n gi\\u1ea3i cao 1920 x 1080px Full HD c&ugrave;ng t\\u1ea5m n\\u1ec1n IPS kh&ocirc;ng ca\\u0309m \\u01b0\\u0301ng mang l\\u1ea1i ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng h&igrave;nh \\u1ea3nh v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng s\\u1eafc n&eacute;t. Trang b\\u1ecb th&ecirc;m HD webcam s\\u1ebd h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 b\\u1ea1n call video ho\\u1eb7c tham gia c&aacute;c bu\\u1ed5i h\\u1ecdp m\\u1eb7t online d\\u1ec5 d&agrave;ng.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<figure><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/storage.googleapis.com\\/teko-gae.appspot.com\\/media\\/image\\/2022\\/3\\/29\\/20220329_a65cba55-18bf-4e2b-b6fb-218df33c5fe2.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/figure>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Vi\\u1ec1n m\\u1ecfng l&agrave;m n&ecirc;n thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1eb9p 