hi\\u1ec1u tab, \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng ch\\u1ea1y n&ecirc;n c\\u0169ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111&aacute;p \\u1ee9ng kh&aacute; t\\u1ed1t.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><strong>Chip \\u0111\\u1ed3 h\\u1ecda Intel Iris Xe Graphics s\\u1eafc n&eacute;t, \\u1ed5 c\\u1ee9ng dung l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng 512Gb<\\/strong><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Chip \\u0111\\u1ed3 h\\u1ecda&nbsp; Intel Iris Xe Graphics \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t&iacute;ch h\\u1ee3p nh\\u1eb1m c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n hi\\u1ec7u su\\u1ea5t m\\u1ed9t c&aacute;ch t\\u1ed1i \\u01b0u nh\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111&aacute;p \\u1ee9ng m\\u1ecdi \\u0111am m&ecirc; s&aacute;ng t\\u1ea1o c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng v\\u1edbi vi\\u1ec7c xu\\u1ea5t h&igrave;nh \\u1ea3nh 4K tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c ph\\u1ea7n m\\u1ec1m \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng nh\\u01b0 Photoshop,... m\\u1ed9t c&aacute;ch chuy&ecirc;n nghi\\u1ec7p v\\u1edbi c&aacute;c t\\u1ef1a game \\u0111&igrave;nh \\u0111&aacute;m nh\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n nay nh\\u01b0 PUBG, LOL,...&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<figure><img alt=\\\"Laptop MSI Modern 15 A11M-1024VN | \\u0110\\u1ed3 h\\u1ecda s\\u1eafc n\\u00e9t\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/storage.googleapis.com\\/teko-gae.appspot.com\\/media\\/image\\/2022\\/3\\/29\\/20220329_4331e148-e617-4055-857a-a794a0c6d820.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/figure>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\u1ed4 c\\u1ee9ng 512Gb SSD M.2 NVMe mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn dung l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng l\\u01b0u tr\\u1eef c\\u1ef1c l\\u1edbn \\u0111\\u1ec3 b\\u1ea1n tho\\u1ea3i m&aacute;i h\\u01a1n khi t\\u1ea3i v\\u1ec1 nhi\\u1ec1u ph\\u1ea7n m\\u1ec1m, t\\u1ef1a game y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch \\u0111\\u1ec3 gi\\u1ea3i tr&iacute;. B\\u1ed9 nh\\u1edb chu\\u1ea9n SSD c&ograve;n n\\u1ed5i b\\u1eadt v\\u1edbi kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng t\\u0103ng t\\u1ed1c qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh kh\\u1edfi \\u0111\\u1ed9ng m&aacute;y, h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 truy c\\u1eadp d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u nhanh h\\u01a1n ch\\u1ec9 m\\u1ea5t v&agrave;i gi&acirc;y.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><strong>Pin 3 cell s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng kh&aacute; l&acirc;u, b&agrave;n ph&iacute;m LED \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 c&aacute;c ph&iacute;m s\\u1ed1<\\/strong><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\u0110\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi chi\\u1ebfc laptop MSI Modern 15 A11M-1024VN n&agrave;y, b\\u1ea1n s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu 3 cell 52Wh, Pin li\\u1ec1n cho t\\u0103ng th\\u1eddi gian s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng laptop h\\u01a1n so v\\u1edbi c&aacute;c d&ograve;ng pin c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr\\u1ecb th\\u1ea5p kh&aacute;c v&agrave; s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng trong kho\\u1ea3ng t\\u1eeb 5-9 ti\\u1ebfng t&ugrave;y v&agrave;o t&iacute;nh ch\\u1ea5t c&ocirc;ng vi\\u1ec7c c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n. Kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng s\\u1ea1c nhanh ch\\u1ec9 kho\\u1ea3ng 3 gi\\u1edd s\\u1ebd gi&uacute;p b\\u1ea1n quay tr\\u1edf l\\u1ea1i l&agrave;m vi\\u1ec7c nhanh ch&oacute;ng h\\u01a1n sau m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n s\\u1ea1c.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<figure><img alt=\\\"Laptop MSI Modern 15 A11M-1024VN | Pin l\\u00e2u b\\u00e0n ph\\u00edm led\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/storage.googleapis.com\\/teko-gae.appspot.com\\/media\\/image\\/2022\\/3\\/29\\/20220329_d9fe9a0c-e511-42b3-bc38-b1b628089e97.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/figure>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Laptop MSI Modern 15 A11M-1024VN s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu kh&ocirc;ng gian b&agrave;n ph&iacute;m tho\\u1ea3i m&aacute;i v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 ph&iacute;m s\\u1ed1. H&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh ph&iacute;m s&acirc;u gi&uacute;p b\\u1ea1n g&otilde; nh\\u1eadp v\\u0103n b\\u1ea3n nhanh ch&oacute;ng v\\u1edbi c\\u1ea3m gi&aacute;c &ecirc;m &aacute;i v&agrave; nhanh nh\\u1ea1y. Hi\\u1ec7u \\u1ee9ng \\u0111&egrave;n LED \\u0111\\u1eb9p m\\u1eaft gi&uacute;p b\\u1ea1n quan s&aacute;t r&otilde; h\\u01a1n trong \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n tr\\u1eddi t\\u1ed1i v&agrave; n&acirc;ng t\\u1ea7m c\\u1ea3m gi&aacute;c m\\u1ed7i khi ch\\u01a1i game.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><strong>C&agrave;i \\u0111\\u1eb7t s\\u1eb5n Windows 10 Home 64-bit, c\\u1ed5ng k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i \\u0111a d\\u1ea1ng<\\/strong><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\u0110\\u1ec3 kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng \\u0111\\u1ee1 t\\u1ed1n chi ph&iacute; l\\u1eafp \