(778, '1', 'sc_admin/product/create', 'POST', '::1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/108.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '{\"kind\":\"0\",\"descriptions\":{\"en\":{\"name\":\"M\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh LCD MSI Optix G27C5 (1920 x 1080\\/VA\\/165Hz\\/1 ms\\/FreeSync)\",\"keyword\":\"M\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh LCD MSI Optix\",\"description\":\"K\\u00edch th\\u01b0\\u1edbc: 27\\\" (1920 x 1080), T\\u1ef7 l\\u1ec7 16:9\",\"content\":\"<h2><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/phongvu.vn\\/man-hinh-may-tinh-scat.03-N001\\\">M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh<\\/a>&nbsp;cong MSI 27&quot; G27C5 mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m h&igrave;nh \\u1ea3nh tuy\\u1ec7t v\\u1eddi v\\u1edbi ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng hi\\u1ec3n th\\u1ecb s\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, n&acirc;ng cao c\\u1ea3m gi&aacute;c \\u0111\\u1eafm ch&igrave;m v&agrave;o tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n. V\\u1edbi m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh cong \\u1ea5n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng ngh\\u1ec7 hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i, MSI 27&quot; G27C5 l&agrave; l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn tuy\\u1ec7t v\\u1eddi m&agrave; c&aacute;c game th\\u1ee7 n&ecirc;n \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0.&nbsp;<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><strong>Thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i \\u1ea5n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng, m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh cong 27 inch s\\u1eafc n&eacute;t&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh cong MSI 27&quot; G27C5 s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu ki\\u1ec3u d&aacute;ng hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i v\\u1edbi c&aacute;c c\\u1ea1nh vi\\u1ec1n ho&agrave;n thi\\u1ec7n tinh t\\u1ebf, k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p ch&acirc;n \\u0111\\u1ebf ch\\u1eef V v\\u1eeba \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o n&acirc;ng \\u0111\\u1ee1 ph\\u1ea7n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh b&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n v\\u1eeba mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn t\\u1ed5ng th\\u1ec3 m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd v&agrave; h&agrave;i h&ograve;a trong m\\u1ecdi kh&ocirc;ng gian, ph&ugrave; h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi tinh th\\u1ea7n gaming \\u0111\\u1ec3 b\\u1ea1n c&oacute; nhi\\u1ec1u c\\u1ea3m h\\u1ee9ng h\\u01a1n.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<figure><img alt=\\\"M\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh cong MSI G27C5| Thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i \\u1ea5n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/storage.googleapis.com\\/teko-gae.appspot.com\\/media\\/image\\/2021\\/12\\/3\\/20211203_d2273515-de94-44e8-b35c-dca98a53ca89.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/figure>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng t\\u1ea5m n\\u1ec1n VA hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i c&oacute; \\u0111\\u1ed9 cong 1500R, k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p vi\\u1ec1n m\\u1ecfng nh\\u1eb1m m\\u1edf r\\u1ed9ng khung h&igrave;nh hi\\u1ec3n th\\u1ecb g\\u1ea7n nh\\u01b0 t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a. T\\u1ea5m n\\u1ec1n cong gi&uacute;p cho tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m nh\\u1eadp vai v&agrave;o tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n tr\\u1edf n&ecirc;n ch&acirc;n th\\u1ef1c h\\u01a1n, nh\\u1edd \\u0111&oacute; b\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd c\\u1ea3m th\\u1ea5y k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i nhi\\u1ec1u h\\u01a1n v\\u1edbi c&aacute;c pha h&agrave;nh \\u0111\\u1ed9ng k\\u1ecbch t&iacute;nh.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<figure><img alt=\\\"M\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh cong MSI G27C5 | M\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh cong 27 inch s\\u1eafc n\\u00e9t\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/storage.googleapis.com\\/teko-gae.appspot.com\\/media\\/image\\/2021\\/12\\/3\\/20211203_d0b4ca22-9d55-4ad1-805d-03f5ba0f6e59.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/figure>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>MSI 27&quot; G27C5 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 \\u0111&ocirc;\\u0323 ph&acirc;n gia\\u0309i 1920 x 1080P (16:9) gi&uacute;p t&aacute;i hi\\u1ec7n h&igrave;nh \\u1ea3nh s\\u1eafc n&eacute;t, chi ti\\u1ebft d\\u01b0\\u1edbi g&oacute;c nh&igrave;n r\\u1ed9ng l&ecirc;n \\u0111\\u1ebfn 178 \\u0111\\u1ed9. Kha\\u0309 n\\u0103ng hi&ecirc;\\u0309n thi\\u0323 ma\\u0300u s\\u0103\\u0301c v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t tr\\u1ed9i 16.7 tri\\u1ec7u m&agrave;u, cung c\\u1ea5p khung h&igrave;nh s\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u1edbi m&agrave;u s\\u1eafc tuy\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1eb9p, cho tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m h&igrave;nh \\u1ea3nh \\u0111&aacute;ng kinh ng\\u1ea1c.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><strong>C&ocirc;ng ngh\\u1ec7 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng b\\u1ed9 FreeSync, tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i si&ecirc;u m\\u01b0\\u1ee3t<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh cong MSI 27&quot; G27C5 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang b\\u1ecb c&ocirc;ng ngh\\u1ec7 FreeSync, gi&uacute;p \\u0111\\u1ed3ng b\\u1ed9 khung h&igrave;nh nh\\u1eb1m lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf \\u0111&aacute;ng k\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng x&eacute; h&igrave;nh (Tearing) ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn g&acirc;y nhi\\u1ec1u kh&oacute; ch\\u1ecbu cho game th\\u1ee7, n&acirc;ng c\\u1ea5p tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m h&igrave;nh \\u1ea3nh m\\u01b0\\u1ee3t m&agrave;, \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o t\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed9ng kh\\u1edbp v\\u1edbi c\\u1ea3nh t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng trong game.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<figure><img alt=\\\"M\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh cong MSI G27C5 | C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng b\\u1ed9 FreeSync\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/storage.googleapis.com\\/teko-gae.appspot.com\\/media\\/image\\/2021\\/12\\/3\\/20211203_2b5287e4-1d6a-4cc6-9f1a-59d34b62ed4a.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/figure>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, t\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 l&agrave;m m\\u1edbi 165Hz k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p th\\u1eddi gian ph\\u1ea3n h\\u1ed3i c\\u1ef1c nhanh 1ms, mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho b\\u1ea1n l\\u1ee3i th\\u1ebf trong c&aacute;c th\\u1ec3 lo\\u1ea1i tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed9ng nhanh nh\\u01b0 game \\u0111ua xe, b\\u1eafn s&uacute;ng g&oacute;c nh&igrave;n th\\u1ee9 nh\\u1ea5t, m&aacute;y bay chi\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ea5u. Nh\\u1eefng lo\\u1ea1i tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i n&agrave;y \\u0111&ograve;i h\\u1ecfi chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed9ng r\\u1ea5t nhanh v&agrave; \\u0111\\u1ed9 ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c cao, v&agrave; MSI G27C5 s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0a b\\u1ea1n v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ed1i th\\u1ee7 v&agrave; gi&agrave;nh chi\\u1ebfn th\\u1eafng.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><strong>H\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 c\\u1ed5ng xu\